This is a child theme for WordPress's default Twenty Ten theme, customized for the DFLL plugin. For more information, go to http://yjsoon.com/dfll-plugin, and follow the link to the theme customization page (at http://yjsoon.com/2011/02/customising-your-wordpress-theme-for-the-df-linked-list-plugin ).

To install, make sure you have Twenty Ten installed in a folder called "twentyten" (or edit style.css to point it to the right place). Then, add this folder to your themes folder, and activate the theme. 